<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dexterity" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dexterity,</orth> nimbleness: <cit><quote>in youth quick bearing and d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1389" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1389</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my admirable d. of wit,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 121</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with as quick d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.286" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 286</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. so obeying appetite,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.5.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 5, 27</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.168" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 1, 168</bibl>. <cit><quote>to post with such d. to incestuous sheets,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.157" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 157</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>